### Gamification Concepts

- Top 10 friend list as social status signal
  - Being in someone’s Top 10 means you physically hang out with them most
  - Visible to both parties; creates positive reinforcement for real-world meetups
- Re-tap streaks (implicit)
  - Frequent mutual tap-ins strengthen the relationship score
  - Analogous to Snapchat streaks but requires physical presence
- Business tap count as loyalty signal
  - Customers can see their own visit history to a business
  - Potential: visible badge or tier on their profile for that business (“Regular at La Carnita”)
- Concert/event scenario:
  - Fans of an artist could be connected through shared Spotify listening data (see Integrations)
  - At a concert, tap-in with other fans to build a niche sub-network of people with shared taste
  - Artist or venue could run promos targeting only fans who are both in the app and at the event

