### Potential Integrations

- Spotify integration (Phase 2+):
  - Pull user’s top artists over last 3 or 6 months
  - Use listening data to surface shared interests between friends or potential connections
  - Example: both you and a new tap-in are in the top 1% of Weeknd listeners
  - Opens a new metric layer for artists/labels: “5,000 verified Weeknd fans in this niche app, all physically active”
  - Artist teams could use this for targeted promotions, presale access, or merch discounts
  - Tradeoff: requires Spotify OAuth and user consent; adds complexity to onboarding

